entry.tran: (面部或身体局部的)抽搐，痉挛
entry.def: If someone has a tic, a part of their face or body keeps making a small uncontrollable movement, for example because they are tired or have a nervous illness.

example.tran: 她左眼处的肌肉出现抽搐。
